title: This is what happens when you compliment Derek Jeter’s wife | Page Six
text:
Flattery will get you everywhere with Derek Jeter .
The former Yankees slugger made a fan’s New Year’s Eve by buying him dinner after the fan complimented Jeter’s wife, model Hannah Jeter .
We hear the couple was dining at Bern’s Steak House in Tampa, Fla., when the fan commented how beautiful the Sports Illustrated model was.
“Most beautiful in the world,” a source overheard Jeter reply. “She is the best decision I have ever made.”
Jeter then generously picked up the man’s bill.
